data.description: Cantamia Beauty! Popular and roomy Sonata plan with numerous custom enhancements. 2 bedrooms, 2 baths with a den/flex room. Spacious living areas with a great room, formal type dining and open kitchen. Porcelain plank flooring, quartz counters, farm sink, kitchen island, walk-in Pantry, custom lighting, upgraded fixtures, electric fireplace, and Builder 8' doors throughout add to the interior design. The primary bath has double sinks, walk-in shower, and private W/C. Dual pane Low E windows. Pro installed rear yard with turf and full desert landscaping. Patio with gas stub. 2 car garage and tankless water heater. Huge laundry room. 55+ gated community! Full community recreation center with too many activities to list.  Live and stay a while. Upgrades added by the Seller: Fireplace, $3,000, Plantation Shutters, $5,000, Interior Lighting, $3,000, Faucets, $600, Cabinet Hardware, $500, Front Yard Landscaping, $1000, Rear Yard Landscaping, $15,000. Total $28,100.
